                  .embed-responsive-item.recommended-item__photo(style={'background-image': 'url(static/images/content/rec.png)'})
                .recommended-item-desc
                  .recommended-item-title.text-big Фритюрница ERGO EF-062
                  .recommended-item-price.mb-2 6 697 <span class="recommended-item-cur">₽/шт</span>
                  .recommended-item__btn-container.d-flex.align-items-center
                    .btn.recommended-item__btn.mr-4
                      +icon('cart', 'mr-2')
                      | В корзину
